      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. A child should be an Indian Citizen.\n1. A child above the age of 5 years and not exceeding 18 years (as of 31st July of respective year).\n1. The act/incident/achievement should have been within 2 years of the last date of receipt of application/nomination for the year of consideration.\n1. The child must have made outstanding contributions in any of the seven categories specified above\n\n  - Bravery.\n  - Art &amp; Culture.\n  - Environment.\n  - Innovation.\n  - Science &amp; Technology.\n  - Social Service.\n  - Sports.\n\n\n",
